		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<div><p>Michael Dell said: “If&nbsp;you are the smartest person in&nbsp;the room, then you are in&nbsp;the wrong room.”</p>

<p>Whatever room you choose in&nbsp;Plarium, you’ll be&nbsp;at&nbsp;the right one, because this company gives you an&nbsp;opportunity to&nbsp;grow and improve your skills every day. You surrounded with the brightest and talented people. <br>Top Managers in&nbsp;Plarium are the reason of&nbsp;the atmosphere where you want to&nbsp;spend 25&nbsp;h per day.</p></div>
		</div>

